            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, remove the<strong> creamed coconut</strong> from the sachet<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> and chop it roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> to the pan with the <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[275ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
